  "aiHints": {
    "analysisContext": "Vectrex ROM: official GCE cartridges begin with 'g GCE YYYY' ASCII copyright string. The 6809 CPU starts at ROM address 0x0000. BIOS (8 KB internal) provides vector drawing subroutines called via JSR. ROM address space: 0x0000-0x7FFF (cartridge, 32 KB max). 0x8000-0xFFFF: BIOS, RAM, hardware registers.",
